---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout title="Mentoring Task Force & Ad Hoc Teams - ROM Business Psychology">

<!-- HERO WITH IMAGE -->
<section class="relative h-[50vh] min-h-[400px] flex items-center overflow-hidden">
  <img
    src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517245386807-bb43f82c33c4?w=1920&q=80"
    alt="Task force meeting"
    class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover"
  />
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-900/90 via-teal-900/70 to-transparent"></div>
  
  <div class="relative z-10 container mx-auto px-6 max-w-[896px]">
    <p class="text-teal-400 font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">
      Teams
    </p>
    <h1 class="text-white text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 leading-tight">
      Mentoring Task Force<br/>& Ad Hoc Teams
    </h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
      Business runs fast. Contemporary complexity requires companies to enlarge their capacity through improving processes, simplifying things, and promoting open communication.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- COMPLEXITY SECTION -->
<section class="bg-white py-20">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-[896px]">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div class="order-2 md:order-1">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-500 to-teal-700 rounded-3xl p-10 text-white">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Why Diversity Matters</h3>
          <p class="text-teal-100 mb-6">
            The fundamental practice of effective decision making is an open and tolerant dialogue among people holding diverse perspectives.
          </p>
          <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-white/30 pl-4 italic text-teal-50">
            "If two people think the same, one of them can be excused."
          </blockquote>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="order-1 md:order-2">
        <p class="text-teal-600 font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">The Reality</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Dealing with Complexity</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Modern organizations are multidisciplinary by nature and operate in highly interdependent environments. To make good calls, they should cultivate an interdisciplinary collaborative culture.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Naturally, diversity is also a source for conflicts and misunderstandings, and might cause waste, negativity, and frustration.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SITUATIONS WE HANDLE -->
<section class="bg-slate-900 py-20">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-[896px]">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <p class="text-teal-400 font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Our Expertise</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Situations We Handle</h2>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <div class="bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-700 hover:border-teal-500 transition-colors">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-teal-500/20 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-teal-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">Cross-Organizational Task Force</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Teams assembled to solve bottlenecks and improve processes</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-700 hover:border-teal-500 transition-colors">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-cyan-500/20 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-cyan-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">Departmental Teams</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Organic teams that wish to alleviate staff meetings and improve collaboration</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-700 hover:border-teal-500 transition-colors">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-500/20 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">Conflict Resolution</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Executives that just don't get along and need facilitation</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- THE PROCESS -->
<section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-50 to-cyan-50 py-20">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-[896px]">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <p class="text-teal-600 font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">How We Work</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">The Mentoring Process</h2>
    </div>
    
    <div class="relative">
      <!-- Timeline line -->
      <div class="hidden md:block absolute left-1/2 top-0 bottom-0 w-0.5 bg-teal-300"></div>
      
      <div class="space-y-12">
        <!-- Step 1 -->
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8">
          <div class="md:w-1/2 md:text-right">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-lg inline-block">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">1. Analysis</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Interviews and systematic observations to understand the situation</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-teal-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold z-10 flex-shrink-0">1</div>
          <div class="md:w-1/2"></div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Step 2 -->
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8">
          <div class="md:w-1/2"></div>
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-teal-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold z-10 flex-shrink-0">2</div>
          <div class="md:w-1/2">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-lg inline-block">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">2. Self-Diagnosis</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Guide stakeholders to map challenges and areas of improvement</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Step 3 -->
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8">
          <div class="md:w-1/2 md:text-right">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-lg inline-block">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">3. Facilitation</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Secure, tight-guided meetings to promote effective dialogue</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-teal-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold z-10 flex-shrink-0">3</div>
          <div class="md:w-1/2"></div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Step 4 -->
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8">
          <div class="md:w-1/2"></div>
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-teal-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold z-10 flex-shrink-0">4</div>
          <div class="md:w-1/2">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-lg inline-block">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">4. Implementation</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Sustainable action items and simple, concise plans</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- OUTCOME -->
<section class="bg-teal-600 py-16">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-[896px] text-center text-white">
    <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4">The Aim</h2>
    <p class="text-xl text-teal-100 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      Increase team effectiveness to meet current as well as future challengesâ€”facilitating communication, ensuring trust, implementing suitable methodologies, and establishing sustainable action plans.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<Footer />
</Layout>
